on player fish:
    if fishing state is fishing:
        send title "&3ðŸŽ£&bðŸŽ£&fðŸŽ£ &bRod casted! &fðŸŽ£&bðŸŽ£&3ðŸŽ£" to player for 3 seconds
    else if fishing state is bite:
